    "## Bag of Words (BoW)\n",
    "\n",
    "The **Bag of Words** model represents a document as a vector of word counts, ignoring word order.\n",
    "Given vocabulary $V$, document $d$ becomes:\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\\mathbf{x}_d = \\bigl[\\text{count}(w_1, d),\\; \\text{count}(w_2, d),\\; \\ldots,\\; \\text{count}(w_{|V|}, d)\\bigr]\n",
    "$$"
   ]
