    "**Limitation**: BoW ignores word order and treats all words equally, including stopwords.\n",
    "\n",
    "## TF-IDF: Weighting by Importance\n",
    "\n",
    "**TF-IDF** downweights frequent words and upweights distinctive ones:\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\\text{TF-IDF}(t, d) = \\frac{\\text{count}(t, d)}{|d|} \\times \\log \\frac{N}{1 + \\text{df}(t)}\n",
    "$$"
   ]
